{"tid":2063613,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"快啲同我入去幫拖！有個黃色channel 開始有5毛攻擊話手足老母係雞但冇人知！","createTime":"2020-06-14T07:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T08:19:06.000Z","uid":315365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dd768584883f485a82926659d7b42516519a1c39","tid":2063613,"uid":315365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:11:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100835348239214/posts/141915300797885/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100835348239214%2Fposts%2F141915300797885%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJtjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=cad4a394\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100835348239214/posts/141915300797885/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CBS78e-Fq42/?igshid=1pyutjj4e3q4l\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCBS78e-Fq42%2F%3Figshid%3D1pyutjj4e3q4l&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJtjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=5186200a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCBS78e-Fq42%2F%3Figshid%3D1pyutjj4e3q4l&h=2db83a14\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CBS78e-Fq42/?igshid=1pyutjj4e3q4l</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">呢個channel 黃到爆！一路都有出唔同類型嘅片做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但冇乜人知<br />\n<br />\n前幾日又出咗條片鼓勵大家堅持落去，點知開始有5毛入侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃嘅channel 真係唔多，希望大家可以一齊支持下佢地！等佢地都唔好放棄！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"585b7d776b9bfa612d538f34d64ec33cc764d162","tid":2063613,"uid":315365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:16:13.000Z","msg":"Push!"},{"pid":"f0b9741f6c8d9bed881ea4fde3d5e3069d6d1907","tid":2063613,"uid":315365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:16:27.000Z","msg":"Push!"},{"pid":"382332f63e15bbbf1f1c63710342f900c88bad9a","tid":2063613,"uid":315365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:16:37.000Z","msg":"Push!"},{"pid":"c3ef58712667bc701323379b5a5bcf8078cb64a1","tid":2063613,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UngcVHa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUngcVHa.jpg&h=5afe454d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1️⃣香港白領(行政及文職)同行工會<br />\n總之你係返office 工都基本上合符入資格（唔清楚自己入唔入到都可先pm問下工會先）<br />\n入會表：<a href=\"http://application.hkwccu.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapplication.hkwccu.org&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJtjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=4e4d1fa2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://application.hkwccu.org</a><br />\n<br />\n2️⃣前線新力量零售工會<br />\n好簡單，做零售的手足都可入，不論你係全職定兼職都入得<br />\n入會表：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Y5UiR9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Y5UiR9&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJtjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=b2364b96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Y5UiR9</a><br />\n<br />\n3️⃣飲食及酒店業職工總會<br />\n都係好簡單，做飲食的手足都可入，你係學生炒下散又好，全職定兼職都入得<br />\n入會表：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/8yK7ZEtZboY45apU7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F8yK7ZEtZboY45apU7&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJtjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=929395da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/8yK7ZEtZboY45apU7</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">入會機會黎喇 <br />\n大學生及兼職打工仔</span></span><br />\n個幾星期 工會人數增長都係得千幾人<br />\n大家踴躍入會 齊齊投票<br />\n入左會先可以公投<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2be8724df2cd285644001ec0fa23ffb74aa7cdf","tid":2063613,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":